---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
---
<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
  <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
    <div class="p-1 rounded-full bg-accent border-4 border-orange-500">
      <img src="/assets/images/profile.png" alt="Sanjay Nair" class="rounded-full w-48 h-48 object-cover">
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Hello! I'm Sanjay Nair. I am a software engineering leader based in Atlanta, Georgia. I enjoy working with
    full stack teams on value driven projects.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    With experience in various technologies and leadership roles, I focus on delivering high-quality software solutions while mentoring and growing engineering teams.
  </p>
</div>

<p class="flex text-center space-x-4"> In my spare time I enjoy reading, writing, and public speaking.</p>

    <hr class="my-12 mx-4 border-gray-700">

    <section class="mt-8 p-4 bg-primary-dark rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-4">Latest Post</h2>
        {% set latestPost = collections.blog | reverse | first %}
        {% if latestPost %}
        <article class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-4 blog-post">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent post-title">
              <a href="{{ latestPost.url }}">{{ latestPost.data.title }}</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-1">
              {{ latestPost.date | date("MMMM d, yyyy") }} • {{ latestPost.data.readingTime }}
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary-blue mb-2">
              Tags: 
              {% for tag in latestPost.data.tags %}
                {% if tag !== "blog" %}
                  <a href="/tags/{{ tag }}" class="mr-1 bg-gray-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-white text-xs post-tag hover:bg-gray-700">{{ tag }}</a>
                {% endif %}
              {% endfor %}
            </p>
            <p class="post-content">{{ latestPost.templateContent | striptags | truncate(150) }}...</p>
            <a href="{{ latestPost.url }}" class="text-accent hover:underline">Read more →</a>
          </article>
        {% endif %}
      </section>

      <footer class="mt-12 text-center text-gray-400 pb-8">
        Made with <span class="text-red-500">❤️</span> by Sanjay Nair
      </footer>